[center][color=yellow][heading]What is Photoreal ENB ?[/heading][/color][/center]

Photoreal ENB is a realistic ENB config using latest ENB version. This preset have nice performance with many graphical mods.

[center][color=yellow][heading]Installation[/heading][/color][/center]

- Install Climates of Tamriel and Realistic Lighting Overhaul !
- Download the lates ENB files by Boris Vorontsov and install it
- Download SweetFX from http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/23364/?
- Download Photoreal ENB
- Play The Game

Recomended Mods:
-Skyrim HD - 2K Textures by NebuLa
-Skyrim Flora Overhaul bu Vurt

My PC:
-Intel Pentium Dual Core 2.5GHZ
-ATI Radeon Asus HD5770 1 GB DDR5 CU Core
-3GB DDR2 RAM


Credits:
-Boris Vorontsov for ENB
-Kyokushinoyama for best shaders
If I have used anyone's files without crediting you please let me know.
